# Location-Based Dynamic Journal Prompts — Full Audit & Plan

The feature should use native iOS Core Location APIs for standard location updates, significant location changes, and region monitoring, with dynamic context-aware prompt generation based on place category, time of day, duration, and visit frequency. The feature should be **opt-out** (enabled by default).

## Audit Results

